com.iopipe

Class PerformanceEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iopipe.PerformanceEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<PerformanceEntry>

    public final class PerformanceEntry
extends Object
implements Comparable<PerformanceEntry>
    This class represents a single performance entry which is used to record the start time and the potential duration of an event.
    Since:
    2018/01/19
